helper-doc

* convert all from ANSI to UTF8 for styling and, after doing this, back to ANSI

# -----------
receive .pas

styling header
   add new header

styling buttons
   remove old buttons
   add new buttons

styling grids
   identify DBGrid
   create the necessary procedure for each one if are not created
   at the start of the procedure or the end (if is already created), write the content accordingly

styling tabs
   identify page controls
   create tab viewer accordingly
   create necessary procedures to the tab viewer
   make necessary callings of tab viewer procedures and page control stylings
   identify all page control or tabs usages and change to the tab viewer model


# -----------
receive .dfm

styling form
   set: Align, BorderStyle, BorderWidth, Ctl3D, Font, Left, Position, Top, Width, WindowState

styling TLabel
   set: Alignment, Font

styling TRadioButton
   set: Alignment, Font

styling TCheckBox
   set: Alignment, Font

styling TEdit
   set: BevelEdges, BevelInner, BevelKind, BevelOuter, BorderStyle, Ctl3D, Font, Height

styling TMSEditSel
   set: BevelEdges, BevelInner, BevelKind, BevelOuter, BorderStyle, Ctl3D, Font, Height

styling TComboBox
   set: BevelEdges, BevelInner, BevelKind, BevelOuter, Ctl3D, Font, Height

styling TMaskEdit
   set: BevelEdges, BevelInner, BevelKind, BevelOuter, BorderStyle, Ctl3D, Font, Height

styling TMSDateEdit
   set: BevelEdges, BevelInner, BevelKind, BevelOuter, BorderStyle, Font, Height

styling TDBGrid
   set: BorderStyle, Color, Ctl3D, FixedColor, ParentColor, ParentCtl3D, ParentFont, ParentShowHint, Font

styling TMSDBGrid
   set: BorderStyle, Color, Ctl3D, FixedColor, ParentColor, ParentCtl3D, ParentFont, ParentShowHint, Font

styling TStringGrid
   set: BorderStyle, Color, Ctl3D, FixedColor, ParentColor, ParentCtl3D, ParentFont, ParentShowHint, Font

styling TPanel
   set: Align, BevelInner, BevelOuter, BorderStyle, Color, Ctl3D, Font

add header
   add header and set default styles

add buttons
   add buttons and set default styles